title: Does Taco Bell Serve ‘Grade D But Edible’ Meat?
subtitle: A rumor held that prisons, school cafeterias, Taco Bell, and other fast food restaurants serve "Grade D but edible" meat.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Prisons, school cafeterias, Taco Bell, and other fast food restaurants use "Grade D but edible" meat in the food products they serve.
